{"tid":978901,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【訂婚三年】「Marvel隊長」貝兒娜森與未婚夫取消婚約","createTime":"2019-01-12T09:15:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T15:09:08.000Z","uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fc9b410d04c6d4456c800f5bd11d21f9a436e7da","tid":978901,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T09:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190112/large/1547261720_9c20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190112%2Flarge%2F1547261720_9c20.jpg&h=b2e0720f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貝兒娜森已跟未婚夫取消婚約。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190112/large/1547261167_cb94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190112%2Flarge%2F1547261167_cb94.jpg&h=87095107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n超級英雄片《Marvel隊長》安排3月上映。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190112/large/1547261167_d31e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190112%2Flarge%2F1547261167_d31e.jpg&h=dab0f8b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貝兒娜森去年11月最後一次上載二人合照。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190112/large/1547261168_39cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190112%2Flarge%2F1547261168_39cd.jpg&h=2b691c87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAlex Greenwald係美國樂隊Phantom Planet主音。<br />\n憑《抖室》（Room）奪得奧斯卡影后嘅29歲女星貝兒娜森（Brie Larson），其主演嘅超級英雄片《Marvel隊長》（Captain Marvel）安排3月上映，但貝兒近日爆出同39歲音樂人男友Alex Greenwald取消婚約，有知情人士指兩人仍保持密切關係。<br />\nAlex Greenwald係美國樂隊Phantom Planet主音，貝兒與拍拖多年嘅Alex於2016年3月在日本旅行時訂婚，同年貝兒亮相日本節目時已被發現戴着訂婚戒指。去年4月，貝兒出席《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》（Avengers: Infinity War）首映禮，Alex亦有陪同出席，月前貝兒亦有喺社交網上載二人合照。<br />\n另外，3月全球開畫嘅《Marvel隊長》來勢洶洶，有預測指該片於北美開畫首周票房高達1.4億至1.8億美元（約10.9億至14億港元），在北美最大票務平台Fandango上，《Marvel隊長》首日預售成績排Marvel電影第三位，僅次於《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》及《黑豹》（Black Panther〉。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190112/59133913\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190112%2F59133913&d=mOYtx0gTspmDMSj35yKdKQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=34df3692\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190112%2F59133913&h=8816bd66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190112/59133913</a>"},{"pid":"d83c0c0956384741dd26e004d454d511a67b2c14","tid":978901,"uid":107364,"like":10,"dislike":10,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T09:16:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0c225995bb5dc707170947bb70402c8296d7e9c","tid":978901,"uid":142351,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T09:16:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc509d778c9b2e9d99824e4b3e8de1c91d200aea","tid":978901,"uid":212399,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T09:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/gpZe4wB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgpZe4wB.png&h=b67e8f2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"065f7b85affbc62a99b12d92327981143625ceb6","tid":978901,"uid":36072,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T09:19:08.000Z","msg":"個年齡係咪調轉咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66a97e825687c09c028173e115d89f4c221efb0","tid":978901,"uid":102880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc509d778c9b2e9d99824e4b3e8de1c91d200aea","tid":978901,"uid":212399,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T09:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/gpZe4wB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%